{"tid":1775550,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今時今日既香港，三罷先係最大殺傷力既武器","createTime":"2019-12-09T02:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T13:49:43.000Z","uid":221360,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2284d95d0cb426d43df31f7a3769b49005c0cb0a","tid":1775550,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:27:30.000Z","msg":"老實講，黎明行動已經冇乜效率...中意返工既照搵方法返，返唔到既照扣人工扣假，其實有咩用？我地個目標唔係咁樣...加上呢招已經out晒，正苦已經有晒plan黎捉人，前線學生唔係condom呀...<br />\n黎明行動而家個效率好低，一黎已經冇乜人會／敢做；二黎d狗有晒佈置，被捕率極高。如果真係要做到三罷既，大家可唔可以諗一諗其他真係對準目標、被捕機率低既行動呀？你個行動愈安全（對行動者），就會愈多人響應。愈多人響應個威力就愈大，就算到時只係狼來了（<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">例如車釘</span></span>），都可以造成威嚇作用。<br />\n我有個小建議，和理非前線都可以做：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加入工會，加入工會，加入工會，加入工會，加入工會！</span></span></strong><br />\n搵返自己個行業入返工會。呢一刻真係做到最有效既長期三罷得一個方法，就係工會聯盟罷工，一黎可以保障到罷工者（例如真係比人炒左，可以搵返自己工會幫手搵工etc.）二黎可以聚集到各行各業。<br />\n當一個人罷工其實真係冇乜用，但如果當每個行業都有一群人罷工既時候，成效就好大，所以希望大家入返自己行業既工會...等待時機揸緊正苦春袋。<br />\n入返三罷group，禁返頂置搵返自己行業既group入返。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">二百萬三罷聯合陣線頻道：</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2Ldebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=6cfe8c82\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n（PS：我唔係三罷group既人，我只係一個普通既香港人...只係覺得呢個行動對而家香港既情況真係最有效既）<br />\n<br />\n最後我想講，黎明行動唔係冇用，只係真正三罷既其中一個行動...如果唔配合埋其他行動既話，成效會好低...我亦都唔想再見到d學生，前線比呢d狼來了post推出去送死。希望大家忍一忍，等待時機再行動。<br />\n（<span style=\"color: purple;\">開post叫人黎明行動果班，唔該你地唔好得把口，你地咁唔想返工既自己罷工又好請病假都好，咪撚害死果前線</span>）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c1eb052479ef353d1a604e937f9e45811d0a16d3","tid":1775550,"uid":221360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:28:25.000Z","msg":"前線唔係condom，加入工會大家都可以做到。"},{"pid":"bcdb093a60c6aeda3f010552738a15a2a0d03e04","tid":1775550,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:29:28.000Z","msg":"近排已經開始多左唔少工會出現，叫埋身邊同事家人朋友都入工會"},{"pid":"6b7027351d192e2cac3b8c9295797bf1ba949446","tid":1775550,"uid":233651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:31:07.000Z","msg":"其實想問，工會有無話組夠幾多人可以發動大罷工？"},{"pid":"66b85710f3fa5a2d7f805ee67e245a37ef1d4811","tid":1775550,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:31:53.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下。<br />\n<br />\n[ 國際戰缐 ] 歐洲巡迴展覧團隊眾籌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b15e64d668fe0a53f819fdbb34601f5f0477df9c","tid":1775550,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf77814524fc43e40930237dbeef5f09fb162a3","tid":1775550,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b7027351d192e2cac3b8c9295797bf1ba949446","tid":1775550,"uid":233651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:31:07.000Z","msg":"其實想問，工會有無話組夠幾多人可以發動大罷工？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:36:22.000Z","msg":"其實我都唔清楚，呢個好似要睇個工會佢地決定，當佈置好晒覺得時機岩既，就可以行動。所以真係好需要大家入工會...冇人入既工會根本就冇可能發動到罷工，我好似講緊廢話咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758cc82fe33d4511a1f66f74e449915525eb33c5","tid":1775550,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66b85710f3fa5a2d7f805ee67e245a37ef1d4811","tid":1775550,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:31:53.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下。<br />\n<br />\n[ 國際戰缐 ] 歐洲巡迴展覧團隊眾籌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:36:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79e5241729250aed360fdf2d50ace0f2393d5982","tid":1775550,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564348cd9992a5eb458cb9c61efe4349769f8a6e","tid":1775550,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:40:48.000Z","msg":"希望大家入返自己工會，唔好咩都要前線幫大家爭取香港本來有既野啦！佢地唔係condom，我地都可以做到野架，要一齊配合呀！"},{"pid":"59fc7a28c3da0409c4e42b69b7e46a8906347717","tid":1775550,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:41:31.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"b6ad660dfb6b81b027b405e406dcacb4f5ddcd90","tid":1775550,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:42:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94821626370e4874f57ae843a21075bde141cc2f","tid":1775550,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:42:42.000Z","msg":"二百萬三罷聯合陣線頻道：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2Ldebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=6cfe8c82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a>"},{"pid":"a48d220f8072d52ae44150fcb63f0842979ed9c6","tid":1775550,"uid":310966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:43:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d8755a58435c260d3aed44987915d12a1ad1805","tid":1775550,"uid":277363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"有時真係唔明你地點諗<br />\n明明呢場運動特色係冇大台<br />\n但工會本身就係中心，大台既一種"},{"pid":"d7d889c18e98ca6047b9afbecc6409dcdbfc20f4","tid":1775550,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d8755a58435c260d3aed44987915d12a1ad1805","tid":1775550,"uid":277363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"有時真係唔明你地點諗<br />\n明明呢場運動特色係冇大台<br />\n但工會本身就係中心，大台既一種"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T03:09:18.000Z","msg":"老實講，你冇一個凝聚點，好難做到大成效。只係呢個凝聚點分散成數以萬點，再集埋一齊行動。冇大台係呢場運動既特色，係因為當初雨革就係比大台瓦解，吸取左教訓，亦都希望各行工會唔好再步入雨革既命運。"},{"pid":"82589fe3e71f0431c60e2479bafb3ef5c1d9c70a","tid":1775550,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T03:12:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"251f7ac24c715e56a9b93c7f5af5a9539e536cc4","tid":1775550,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T03:14:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"473cac92fc7bffca1aa126987c3c3d7f897cf644","tid":1775550,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:49:43.000Z","msg":"推!"}]}